org.hibernate.sql.ast.produce.spi

Interface SqlAstFunctionProducer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SqmExpression, SqmFunction, SqmNode, SqmSelectableNode, SqmTypedNode, SqmVisitableNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocateEmulationUsingPositionAndSubstring.PositionFunction, NvlFunctionTemplate.SqmNvlFunction, org.hibernate.query.sqm.produce.function.internal.SelfRenderingSqmFunction, SqmJdbcFunctionEscapeWrapper

    public interface SqlAstFunctionProducer
extends SqmFunction
    Contract for functions impls that would like to control the translation of the SQM expression into the SQL AST function

    convertToSqlAst(org.hibernate.sql.ast.produce.sqm.spi.SqmToSqlAstConverter) is the main contract here. It will be called as we walk the SQM tree to generate SQL AST and asked to produce the equivalent SQL AST expression
